metadata.name: ASRAYA Genesis
metadata.description: Our Genesis artwork depicts the original act of creation. Pure Source energy emanating from the zero point into the physical realm, giving birth to life. Masculine and feminine forms emerging from the primordial oceans, contemplating their own existence through perceiving the motion of counterbalancing pyramids. A rainbow spectrum infuses this emergence, granting vibrancy and depth to the androgynous form. Each ray, a unique expression of the infinite, together, creating a bridge to higher octaves of awareness. Your Genesis NFT is a rare artifact with only 144 ever minted, with each piece destined to increase in value and utility, serving as a master key to unlock your supreme potential.
